  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The goal of our study is to correlate data from non-invasive tests such as perfusion lung
      scans with hemodynamic measurements from right heart catherizations.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Data collected from PAH patients who have had non-invasive Ventilation/Perfusion testing,
      Echocardiography, Chest CT Scan, Pulmonary Function Testing and the correlation of those
      results to the hemodynamic parameters Right Heart Catherization results and the various
      biomarkers.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
